<div class="jumbotron-m">


    <header>

        <h2><b>SELECT STAGE</b></h2>

        <h4><i>Please select the stage of your project, at which you want to perofrm estimatimation.</i></h4>

    </header>


    <br />
    <br />


    <div class="row">

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">

                <div class="panel-body ">

                    <h3 class="text-center text-blue"><b> BASIC STAGE </b></h3>
                    <hr />
                    <p class="text-small text-black">
                        1. It's applied early in the project.<br />
                        2. It computes effort as a function of program size, Estimate the project parameters, Basic stage would provide a quick and early approximation of software cost.

                    </p>


                </div>



                <p class="text-center">   @Html.ActionLink("SELECT", "SelectMode", "COCOMOI", new { Stage = "Basic Stage" }, new { @class = "btn btn-default btn-blue" })</p>




            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-md-4">
            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-body">

                    <h3 class="text-center text-blue"><b> INTERMEDIATE STAGE </b></h3>
                    <hr />

                    <p class="text-small text-black">
                        1. It's applied after requirements acquisition.<br />
                        2. The intermediate stage computes effort as a function of size and a set of cost drivers.
